y.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELife%20after%20graduating%20college%20in%202019%20meant%20bouncing%20from%20job%20to%20job%2C%20burning%20myself%20out%20at%20each%20one.%20Getting%20furloughed%20during%20the%20pandemic%20didn't%20help%2C%20but%20I%20eventually%20started%20working%20odd%20gigs%20again%20and%20auditioning%20for%20acting%20roles.%20There%20were%20times%20when%20I%20would%20struggle%20financially%2C%20then%20do%20okay%2C%20then%20struggle%2C%20then%20do%20okay.%20It%20was%20a%20pattern%20that%20I%20hated%2C%20but%20a%20pattern%20I%20was%20used%20to.%20It%20was%20so%20stressful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220242ecdc-e06f-48f2-a8d8-fb679aedfb9a%5C%22%3EThe%20job%20came%20at%20the%20right%20time%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20at%20my%20lowest%20year%20personally%2C%20a%20friend%20referred%20me%20to%20Same%20Ole%20Line%20Dudes%2C%20a%20company%20that%20pays%20people%20to%20wait%20in%20lines%20on%20their%20behalf.%20My%20first%20gig%20was%20a%20Jimmy%20Choo%20sample%20sale%20in%20October%20of%202023.%20When%20I%20first%20got%20the%20Google%20Invite%20form%20for%20the%20job%2C%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20scam.%20All%20I%20had%20to%20do%20was%20show%20up%20and%20sit%20in%20line%2C%20and%20I'd%20get%20paid%20around%20%2474.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20only%20planning%20to%20be%20there%20for%20four%20hours%2C%20but%20I%20relooped%20to%20the%20back%20of%20the%20line%20for%20another%20client%20and%20made%20extra%20money.%20I%20basically%20got%20addicted%2C%20and%20soon%2C%20I%20was%20hustling.%20Once%20the%20company%20figured%20out%20I%20was%20in%20it%20for%20the%20long%20run%20and%20was%20broke%2C%20they%20kept%20calling%20me%20back%20for%20more%20sample%20sales%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Folsen-the-row-sample-sale-line-quiet-luxury-l2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EThe%20Row%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Versace%2C%20McQueen.%20You've%20got%20to%20understand%20what%2074%20bucks%20was%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221966%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gigi%20Principe%20at%20260%20sample%20sale%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691cb44ce1a9cbb014de6f06%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221070%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPrincipe%20sat%20for%20many%20sample%20sales%20at%20the%20beginning.%3Cp%3EGigi%20Principe%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20my%20previous%20job%2C%20I%20had%20a%20moment%20where%20I%20wished%20someone%20would%20pay%20me%20to%20do%20nothing%2C%20and%20then%20boom.%20I%20didn't%20mind%20sitting%20out%20in%20the%20winter.%20Bring%20a%20blanket!%20It%20was%20sample%20sale%2C%20sample%20sale%2C%20sample%20sale%2C%20then%20Lucali's%2C%20a%20pizza%20place%20in%20Brooklyn%20that%20doesn't%20take%20reservations.%20It%20was%20a%20top%20restaurant%20for%20us%20at%20the%20time%2C%20so%20getting%20that%20job%20was%20a%20sign%20I'd%20made%20it%20in%20the%20company.%20Lucali's%20cost%20%2432%20an%20hour%2C%20and%20it%20was%20easy%20peasy%20to%20put%20someone's%20name%20down.%20I%20knew%20my%20way%20around%20Brooklyn%20and%20kept%20coming%20back%20despite%20the%20cold%2C%20because%2C%20again%2C%20I%20was%20broke!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222cce4eb8-5b8a-4036-b812-cc5d2dca6c5b%5C%22%3EJobs%20got%20bigger%20and%20bigger%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20managers%20started%20rewarding%20me%2C%20and%20eventually%2C%20they%20brought%20me%20on%20full%20time.%20I%20think%20I%20spent%20almost%20every%20day%20of%202024%20line-sitting.%20Donald%20Trump's%20trial%20was%20huge%20for%20us%20%E2%80%94%20I%20would%20line%20sit%20from%204%20a.m.%20to%208%20a.m.%2C%20or%20sometimes%20midnight%20to%208%20a.m.%2C%20and%20then%20take%20the%20subway%20to%20my%20day%20job%20uptown.%20There%20were%20days%20I%20might%20have%20bailed%20if%20I%20hadn't%20had%20my%20tent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221092%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Same%20Ole%20Line%20Dudes%20sign%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691cb3aee1a9cbb014de6ee7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221446%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPrincipe%20brings%20supplies%2C%20like%20chairs%20and%20tents%2C%20with%20her%20to%20wait%20in%20line.%3Cp%3EGigi%20Principe%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20did%20the%20Daniel%20Penny%20trial%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluigi-mangione-unitedhealth-ceo-killing-person-what-to-know-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELuigi%20Mangione%3C%2Fa%3E%20trial%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiddy-personal-assistant-david-james-george-kaplan-trial-testimony-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDiddy%20trial%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20can't%20talk%20about%20my%20clients%2C%20but%20I've%20sat%20for%20the%20press%2C%20lawyers%2C%20and%20the%20public.%20Sometimes%2C%20I%20travel%20for%20clients.%20(We%20charge%20for%20travel%20time%2C%20and%20clients%20pay%20for%20the%20tickets.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228bad0511-1d80-4a6a-bc41-735f8cbc27f3%5C%22%3EHow%20people%20spend%20says%20a%20lot%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHourly%20rates%20depend%20on%20the%20event%20%E2%80%94%20sometimes%20%2425%2C%20sometimes%20%2432%2C%20sometimes%20%2450%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I've%20been%20getting%20commission%20since%20I%20became%20a%20manager%20in%20March.%20This%20job%20is%20hard%2C%20it's%20taxing%20on%20the%20body%2C%20but%20it%20saved%20my%20life%2C%20and%20it%20really%20helps%20people.%20I%20get%20paid%20to%20wait%2C%20but%20also%20to%20watch%20wrestling%20videos%2C%20or%20write%2C%20or%20rest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20money%20keeps%20flowing%20in%2C%20and%20that's%20also%20taught%20me%20a%20lot%20about%20what%20people%20are%20willing%20to%20pay%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20people%20will%20pay%20a%20lot%20for%20convenience.%20That's%20clear%20when%20I'm%20traveling%20and%20people%20pay%20for%20my%20plane%20tickets%2C%20train%20tickets%2C%20or%20rental%20cars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20