bs%20he%20doesn't%20want%20to%20do.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20top%20trends%20among%20A-listers%20include%20holograms%20and%20hyper-local%20cuisine.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20fell%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluxury-event-planner-clients-over-the-top-indulgent-events-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eevent%20planning%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20accident%20%E2%80%94%20tripped%20and%20landed%20in%20the%20mud%2C%20really.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20decades%20later%2C%20I'm%20still%20dusting%20myself%20off%20and%20loving%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20then%2C%20I%20was%20working%20for%20one%20of%20the%20early%20online-publishing%20companies.%20When%20they%20acquired%20another%20firm%20in%20Cleveland%2C%20they%20shut%20down%20the%20California%20division%2C%20and%20I%20suddenly%20found%20myself%20unemployed%2C%20newly%20married%2C%20first%20child%20on%20the%20way%2C%20and%20panicking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20friend%2C%20the%20director%20of%20catering%20at%20a%20hotel%2C%20listened%20to%20me%20whine%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-moved-hamptons-of-england-cotswolds-luxury-deli-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecatering%20manager%3C%2Fa%3E%20just%20quit.%20Come%20work%20with%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20laughed.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20do%20I%20know%20about%20catering%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20teach%20you%20food.%20I%20can't%20teach%20you%20contracts%20or%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeeding%20a%20paycheck%2C%20I%20said%20yes.%20Within%20six%20months%2C%20I%20learned%20that%20brides%2C%20their%20mothers%2C%20and%20chefs%20were%20a%20volatile%20mix%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20I%20was%20not%20built%20to%20referee%20that%20trio.%20But%20I%20loved%20hospitality%2C%20so%20I%20moved%20into%20hotel%20sales.%20That%20job%20introduced%20me%20to%20professional%20event%20planners.%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20the%20industry%20even%20existed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227b4deda0-35b0-4c3e-8d20-af98e34f6b42%5C%22%3EFrom%20theater%20kid%20to%20event%20producer%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20my%20childhood%20in%20the%20theater%20%E2%80%94%20acting%2C%20stage%20managing%2C%20and%20building%20sets.%20Event%20planning%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20new%20version%20of%20that%3A%20someone%20gives%20me%20a%20script%2C%20I%20cast%20it%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarina-skye-set-designer-music-21-savage-janelle-monae-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edesign%20the%20set%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20direct%20the%20lighting%2C%20and%20make%20sure%20the%20audience%20feels%20something.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20realization%20changed%20everything.%20Once%20I%20joined%20the%20planning%20side%2C%20my%20career%20just%20exploded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20I've%20worked%20with%20high-profile%20companies%20and%20private%20clients%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fariana-grande-net-worth-how-she-makes-her-money%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAriana%20Grande%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Nick%20Jonas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20stage%20of%20my%20career%2C%20I%20say%20no%20more%20often%20than%20I%20say%20yes.%20I%20choose%20clients%20who%20share%20my%20ethics%20and%20understand%20that%20my%20job%20isn't%20to%20be%20a%20servant%20but%20to%20be%20of%20service.%20You%20hire%20me%20for%20my%20expertise%20and%20unique%20perspective.%20If%20you're%20looking%20for%20someone%20to%20agree%20with%20everything%2C%20I'm%20not%20the%20right%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20team%20jokes%20that%20I'm%20the%20love%20child%20of%20Martha%20Stewart%20and%20Anthony%20Bourdain%3A%20I%20can%20make%20things%20exquisitely%20beautiful%20and%20on%20brand%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I'll%20walk%20out%20if%20a%20client%20crosses%20a%20line.%20I%20have%20opinions.%20I'm%20direct.%20But%20that's%20why%20people%20trust%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20run%20my%20pricing%20like%20a%20law%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblack-woman-architecture-left-corporate-america-happy-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Earchitecture%20firm%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20you%20pay%20for%20my%20intellectual%20property%20and%20my%20team's%20time.%20Everything%20else%20is%20a%20pass-through%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20we%20rent%20furniture%20or%20hire%20a%20caterer%2C%20you'll%20see%20the%20exact%20costs.%20I'd%20rather%20a%20client%20sign%20vendor%20contracts%20directly%20than%20suspect%20hidden%20profit%20margins.%20My%20reputation%20is%20all%20I%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECould%20I%20charge%20six%20figures%20for%20every%20event%3F%20Sure%20%E2%80%94%20and%20sometimes%20the%20numbers%20get%20there.%20But%20I%20can't%20hand%20someone%20a%20million-dollar%20invoice%20with%20a%20straight%20face%20unless%20the%20value%20is%20real.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20push%20clients%20to%20incorporate%20community%20give-backs%20into%20their%20celebrations.%20If%20you're%20spending%20that%20much%20money%2C%20something%20good%20should%20ripple%20out%20from%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f8921f62-96d5-4c98-b88e-04c7ea5a497b%5C%22%3EWhat's%20in%20%E2%80%94%20and%20what's%20tired%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20describe%20an%20event%20you%20saw%20on%20%26quot%3BPage%20Six%2C%26quot%3B%20I'll%20stop%20you%20mid-sentence.%20That%20was%20someone%20else's%20idea%2C%20for%20someone%20else's%20story.%20Let's%20find%20out%20what%20moved%20you%20and%20build%20from%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlease%2C%20no%20more%20white-marble%20bars%20and%20faux-mid-century%20%26quot%3Bmodern%26quot%3B%20d%C3%A9cor.%20We%20had%20a%20golden%20opportunity%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20to%20reinvent%20how%20people%20gather%2C%20but%20most%20of%20the%20industry%20reverted%20to%20the%20same%20old%20formula%3A%20long%20tables%2C%20centerpieces%2C%20and%20predictable%20menus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trend%20I%20love%20most%20is%20local%2C%20local%2C%20local%20%E2%80%94%20s