20six%20figures%20in%20a%20single%20livestream.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESuccess%20in%20live%20selling%20boils%20down%20to%20community%20engagement%20and%20generating%20excitement%20around%20products.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20watched%20TV%20at%20odd%20hours%20in%20the%201990s%20and%20early%202000s%2C%20you%20probably%20remember%20QVC%2C%20the%20home%20shopping%20network%20selling%20viewers%20everything%20from%20kitchen%20appliances%20to%20kids'%20toys%2C%20often%20for%20several%20%26quot%3Beasy%26quot%3B%20payments%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20there's%20a%20new%20age%20version%20of%20that%20phenomenon%20that's%20found%20a%20home%20on%20TikTok%20and%20other%20platforms%2C%20but%20instead%20of%20broadcasting%20for%20an%20hour%20between%20the%20nightly%20news%20and%20sitcom%20reruns%2C%20some%20sellers%20are%20streaming%20for%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20also%20be%20incredibly%20lucrative%20if%20you%20find%20the%20right%20niche.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELive%20selling%20on%20platforms%20like%20TikTok%2C%20YouTube%2C%20and%20Instagram%20combines%20livestreaming%20and%20e-commerce.%20Sellers%20are%20hosting%20live%20%26quot%3Bshows%26quot%3B%20and%20chatting%20with%20their%20audience%20in%20real%20time%2C%20while%20viewers%20are%20buying%20directly%20from%20the%20stream%20without%20leaving%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20QVC%20to%20a%20new%20generation%2C%26quot%3B%20e-commerce%20veteran%20Leo%20Limin%2C%20who%20started%20selling%20smart%20light%20bulbs%20on%20Amazon%20in%20the%20mid-2010s%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BSome%20brands%20sell%20through%20thousands%20and%20thousands%20of%20items%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20a%20couple%20of%20hours%2C%20like%20%2450%2C000%20worth%20of%20products%2C%20for%20example%2C%20in%20two%20hours.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHarry%20Luu%20is%20one%20of%20those%20sellers.%20He%20brought%20in%20%2442%2C000%20in%20one%20day%20by%20selling%20two%20rare%20plants%20%E2%80%94%20one%20for%20%2426%2C000%20and%20the%20other%20for%20%2416%2C000%20%E2%80%94%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpalmstreet.app%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPalmstreet%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20live%20shopping%20app%20for%20rare%20plants%20and%20other%20unique%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20call%20myself%20a%20plantdemic%20baby%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20former%20mathematician.%20%26quot%3BDuring%20COVID%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20picked%20up%20a%20hobby%20of%20some%20sort%2C%20and%20plants%20were%20my%20escape%20at%20the%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20plant%20collection%20and%20cultivation%20hobby%20quickly%20evolved%20into%20a%20lucrative%20side%20hustle%20and%2C%20eventually%2C%20a%20sustainable%20career.%20He%20left%20academia%20in%202024%20to%20run%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplantzaddytherapy.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPlant%20Zaddy%20Therapy%3C%2Fa%3E%20full-time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224105%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22harry%20luu%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F692717ade1a9cbb014df07dd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223079%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHarry%20Luu%20cultivates%20and%20sells%20rare%20plants%20on%20a%20platform%20called%20Palmstreet.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Harry%20Luu%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EClinton%20Benninghoff%20runs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ghqmidland.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGolf%20Headquarters%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Midland-based%20brick-and-mortar%20store%20that%20sells%20golf%20apparel%20and%20equipment.%20Last%20summer%2C%20after%20hearing%20about%20an%20auction-style%20platform%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatnot.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhatnot%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20downloaded%20the%20app%20out%20of%20curiosity.%20He%20signed%20up%20to%20be%20a%20seller%20and%2C%20using%20his%20iPhone%2C%20set%20up%20his%20first%20stream%20from%20his%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20set%20up%20the%20camera%20by%20my%20door%2C%20pointed%20it%20toward%20all%20my%20bags%20full%20of%20golf%20clubs%2C%20and%20clicked%20to%20go%20live.%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20what%20I%20was%20doing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BThat%20first%20day%2C%20I%20think%20I%20was%20live%20for%20like%2020%20minutes.%20I%20sold%20a%20putter%2C%20and%20everybody%20in%20my%20stream%20was%20actually%20telling%20me%20how%20to%20stream.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELess%20than%20a%20year%20later%2C%20in%20February%202025%2C%20he%20sold%20over%20%24100%2C000%20in%20products%20in%20a%20six-hour%20live%20show%2C%20a%20Whatnot%20record%20at%20the%20time%20in%20the%20golf%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverybody%20was%20recording%20on%20their%20phones%20when%20we%20finally%20hit%20it.%20I%20was%20so%20hoarse.%20I%20didn't%20have%20a%20voice%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20recalled.%20%26quot%3BThat%20February%208%20show%20let%20us%20know%20that%20we%20can%20do%20this%20at%20a%20high%20level.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20confirmed%20the%20claims%20made%20by%20each%20seller%20featured%20by%20reviewing%20screenshots%20of%20their%20sales%20dashboards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bb8bfc2c-ef2c-4eba-9bfd-0f9509ead2b5%5C%22%3EThe%20unique%20advantage%20of%20live%20selling%3A%20Convenience%20plus%20knowing%20exactly%20what%20you're%20getting%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20joining%20Palmstreet%2C%20Luu%20said%20that%20he%20and%20other%20plant%20collectors%20primarily%20listed%20their%20products%20on%20Facebook.%20But%2C%20as%20live%20selling%20platforms%20started%20to%20gain%20traction%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere%20were%20quite%20a%20few%20of%20us%20who%20migrated%2C%20because%20it%20was%20a%20lot%20faster%2C%20it%20was%20a%20lot%20easier%2C%20and%20it%20was%20a%20lot%20more%20interactive%20and%20fun.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESelling%20online%20is%20loads%20cheaper%20than%20owning%20and%20operating%20a%20brick-and-mortar%20%E2%80%94%20and%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20platform%20you're%20using%2C%20potentially%20easier%20to%20acquire%20customers%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20open%20a%20store%2C%20you%20are%20still%20subject%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20people%20have%20to%20walk%20into%20your%20store.%20When%20you're%20on%20a%20major%20platform%20such%20as%20Palmstreet%2C%20and%20they%20have%20already%20built%20up%20a%20good%20enough%20clientele%2C%20you%20have%20a%20lot%20more%20walk-ins%2C%20quote%20unquote.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBenninghoff%20said%20that%20during%20his%20most-viewed%20Whatnot%20stream%2C%20he%20had%201%2C600%20potential%20buyers%20in%20the%20room.%20He%20has%20sold%20and%20shipped%20products%20to%20buyers%20across%20the%20lower%2048%20states%2C%20as%20well%20as%20in%20Hawaii%2C%20Alaska%2C%20Puerto%20Rico%2C%20and%20South%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20you%20don't%20get%20the%20same%20face-to-face%20interaction%20as%20you%20do%20with%20a%20brick-and-mortar%2C%20and%20customers%20can't%20pick%20up%20products%20with%20their%20two%20hands%2C%20but%20it's%20the%20next%20best%20thing.%20Consumers%20can%20ask%20questions%20in%20real%20time%20and%20see%20the%20product%20from%20all%20angles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20gives%20you%20the%20convenience%20of%20being%20at%20home%2C%20but%20also%20allows%20the%20buyer%20the%20flexibility%20of%20actually%20interacting%20and%20clarifying%20before%20they%20pull%20the%20trigger%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Luu.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20think%20that%20is%20one%20of%20the%20greatest%20advantages%20of%20live%20selling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20every%20e-commerce%20business%20has%20bought%20in.%20Jonathan%20Cohen%2C%20the%20CMO%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-start-an-ecommerce-company-launch-on-amazon-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwo%20eight-figure%20Amazon%20brands%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20uses%20TikTok%20live%2C%20but%20not%20because%20he%20thinks%20it's%20the%20wave%20of%20the%20future%20or%20even%20a%20particularly%20effective%20way%20to%20move%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20live%20selling%2C%20not%20so%20much%20to%20generate%20huge%20amounts%20of%20revenue%2C%20but%20to%20talk%20to%20our%20customers.%20We%20get%20our%20R%26amp%3BD%20and%20our%20customer%20feedback%20directly%20from%20people%20who%20are%20inside%20our%20live%20chat%20rooms%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20and%20warns%20against%20putting%20all%20of%20your%20eggs%20in%20the%20live%20selling%20basket.%20%26quot%3BI%20wouldn't%20say%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20any%20single%20person's%20ticket%20to%20success.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d635e63a-7577-4e72-80b5-de58048bbc53%5C%22%3EWhat%20it%20takes%20to%20succeed%20as%20a%20live%20seller%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EBenninghoff%20describes%20Whatnot%20as%20%26quot%3Ban%20entertainment%20app%26quot%3B%20as%20much%20as%20it%20is%20a%20marketplace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20building%20this%20community%20of%20people%20that%20are%20following%20a%20personality%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20part-time%20pastor%2C%20who%20thrives%20in%20a%20public%20speaking%20environment.%20For%20him%2C%20setting%20up%20a%20camera%20and%20talking%20to%20strangers%20came%20naturally.%20It%20was%20the%20juggling%20of%20multiple%20pieces%20that%20took%20some%20getting%20used%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20biggest%20learning%20curve%20was%20how%20to%20run%20an%20auction%20and%20stay%20engaged%20with%20people%20that%20are%20asking%20questions%20in%20the%20chat%20while%20holding%20up%20the%20item%20at%20the%20right%20angle%20and%20just%20doing%20it%20all%20at%20the%20same%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20helps%20to%20be%20extroverted%20and%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bperformer%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Luu%2C%20who%20had%20experience%20managing%20large%20Zoom%20lectures%20in%20his%20previous%20career%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20essential.%20%26quot%3BDifferent%20people%20resonate%20with%20different%20people.%20You%20will%20inherently%20attract%20your%20own%20crowd.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22casey%20wehr%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6927192ae1a9cbb014df083b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECasey%20Wehr%20started%20streaming%20on%20Whatnot%20with%20his%20two%20sons%2C%20who%20discovered%20the%20platform%20and%20convinced%20him%20to%20use%20it%20to%20sell%20sports%20cards.%3Cp%3ECroutesy%20of%20Casey%20Wehr%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECasey%20Wehr%2C%20who%20works%20full-time%20at%20a%20private%20equity%20firm%20and%20has%20built%20a%20seven-figure%20side%20hustle%20selling%20sports%20cards%20with%20his%20two%20sons%20on%20Whatnot%2C%20has%20mastered%20the%20art%20of%20building%20excitement%20throughout%20live%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20main%20ways%20he's%20earning%20money%20on%20Whatnot.%20There's%20the%20live%20auction%20format%2C%20in%20which%20he'll%20grab%20an%20item%2C%20put%20it%20in%20front%20of%20the%20camera%2C%20and%20start%20a%2015-second%20auction.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20fast%20paced%2C%20it's%20fun%2C%20it's%20engaging%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EViewers%20can%20also%20buy%20packs%20of%20cards%20directly%20from%20his%20store%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatnot.com%2Fuser%2Fkrunk_cards%3Fsrsltid%3DAfmBOoq5SrSJu7n2uZAvNYyFg0UjDPd1wbqYbJDxXvPo4RukZWBzkASq%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKrunk%20Cards%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20at%20any%20point%20during%20the%20stream%2C%20and%20he'll%20do%20a%20%26quot%3Bsealed%20wax%20opening%26quot%3B%20on%20camera.%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20fun%20about%20the%20sealed%20wax%20is%20that%20it's%20a%20community%20event.%20It's%20fun%20to%20open%20product%20just%20when%20you%20go%20buy%20it%20from%20the%20store%20and%20take%20it%20home%2C%20but%20there's%20a%20whole%20other%20level%20of%20excitement%20opening%20a%20box%20with%20100%20other