5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20efforts%20led%20to%20his%20inclusion%20in%20the%20first%20Air%20Pollution%20Task%20Force%20established%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Government.%20This%20task%20force%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20launching%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20landmark%20odd-even%20traffic%20initiative%20in%202015%2C%20aimed%20at%20reducing%20vehicular%20emissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F251663%2Finnovation-toxic-air-pollution-covid-19-ac-filter-fitting-cost-how-to-buy-online-delhi-information-jai-dhar-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebattle%20against%20air%20pollution%20%3C%2Fa%3Ealso%20inspired%20him%20to%20create%20solutions%20through%20his%20venture%2C%20Nirvana%20Being.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20continued%20to%20advocate%20for%20clean%20air%2C%20he%20came%20to%20the%20realisation%20that%20expecting%20significant%20improvements%20in%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20air%20quality%20within%20his%20lifetime%20was%20unlikely.%20This%20prompted%20him%20to%20seek%20out%20a%20place%20where%20both%20the%20air%20and%20quality%20of%20life%20would%20be%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CI%20always%20dreamt%20of%20being%20a%20chowkidar%20(watchman)%20of%20the%20forests%20in%20India.%20I%20have%20no%20hope%20of%20better%20living%20conditions%20in%20Delhi%20or%20Mumbai.%20The%20air%20is%20toxic%20everywhere.%20I%20want%20to%20improve%20my%20own%20quality%20of%20life%2C%20and%20the%20way%20to%20do%20that%20is%20by%20living%20with%20nature%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jai%20tells%20The%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20Delhi%20resident%2C%20he%20often%20visited%20the%20Rajaji%20Tiger%20Reserve%2C%20where%20he%20developed%20a%20deep%20affection%20for%20the%20wildlife.%20Naturally%2C%20when%20it%20came%20time%20to%20find%20a%20place%20t